---
// Solana intro section with premium branded style
---

<section
  class="py-24 bg-[#F8F5FF] relative overflow-hidden border-b-2 border-dashed border-gray-300"
  id="que-es-solana"
>
  <!-- Branded background accents -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#9945FF]/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#14F195]/10 rounded-full blur-[100px]"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left Content Area -->
      <div>
        <h4
          class="text-xs font-bold text-[#9945FF] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4"
        >
          La Red de Mayor Rendimiento
        </h4>
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tight"
        >
          ¿Qué es <span
            class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#9945FF] to-[#14F195]"
            >Solana</span
          >?
        </h2>
        <div
          class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#9945FF] to-[#14F195] rounded-full mb-8"
        >
        </div>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Solana es una blockchain diseñada para la adopción masiva. Es una red
          de alto rendimiento que permite transacciones digitales <span
            class="text-[#9945FF] font-bold"
            >rápidas, seguras y extremadamente económicas</span
          >.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">
          <div
            class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-[#9945FF]/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
          >
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-1">Impacto</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
              Impulsa miles de aplicaciones descentralizadas globales.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-[#9945FF]/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
          >
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-1">Escala</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
              Pagos instantáneos, juegos masivos y finanzas Web3.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://solana.com/es/learn"
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-[#9945FF] hover:bg-[#8338EB] text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-2xl font-black tracking-wide transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-xl shadow-purple-200 uppercase text-sm"
        >
          FORJA TU CAMINO
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M14 5l7 7-7 7M3 12h18"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Area - Premium visual cards -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Floating ambient glow -->
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#9945FF] to-[#14F195] opacity-20 blur-[80px] rounded-full animate-pulse"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="relative grid gap-4 sm:gap-6">
          <!-- Feature Card 1 -->
          <div
            class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
              <div
                class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#9945FF] to-[#CC22FF] flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg overflow-hidden relative group"
              >
                <span class="relative z-10 font-black text-xl">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-xl tracking-tight">
                  Velocidad Extrema
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium">
                  Confirmaciones en milisegundos reales.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature Card 2 -->
          <div
            class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-xl sm:ml-12 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
              <div
                class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#14F195] flex items-center justify-center text-gray-900 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden"
              >
                <span class="relative z-10 font-black text-xl">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-xl tracking-tight">
                  Cero Barreras
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium">
                  Costos ínfimos para cualquier usuario.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature Card 3 -->
          <div
            class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
              <div
                class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#14F195] to-[#9945FF] flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden"
              >
                <span class="relative z-10 font-black text-xl">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-xl tracking-tight">
                  Eco-Consiente
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium">
                  Eficiencia energética de nivel mundial.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
